This is an ongoing project in which I am constructing and programming a surgical robot to play the game operation.
The design utilizes both an arduino and rasperry pi in conjuction to identify objects and remove them.

The folder currently holds the code that allows the robot to move to a specific coordinate in the X,Y plane as well as the circuit
diagram and proposed control algorithm. 

The folder is missing the computer vision half of the program currently

